name: DogeFood
public_notice: DogeFood has recently migrated to a new contract address (0x1bec41a36356d5574aeb068b599ab7e48dd008b8). For more information, kindly visit: https://twitter.com/DogeFood_bsc/status/1483236159358570498?s=20

description.en:
This is a charity dog protection project. We are committed to making a dog charity organization to help every stray dog build their home.
This project will gather: NFTs, gamefi, mining, swap concepts.
We are building a stong community in the beginning of the DogeFood, finding more consensus in order to stabilize the team funding for furter development of Dog charity.
